This paper discusses data management applications that require integrating data from multiple sources and resolving conflicts. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). However, since the paper focuses on data fusion and accuracy of truth discovery, cs.DB and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories. The other sub-categories are also relevant but to a lesser extent.
